									<div class="meta__text">
										<ul>
											<li>As a user, I want to be able to edit the content in the CMS.</li>
										</ul>
									</div>
									<span class="meta__notes"><i class="fa fa-sticky-note"></i> Notes</span>
									<div class="meta__text">
										Applicable to all BEE content types:
										<ul>
											<li><strong>PAGE</strong>: News Story, Blog, Partner Story, Wire story, Press Release, Breaking News, Gallery, Quiz, Poll, Catchall Page, Series, Season, Episode, Promo</li>
											<li><strong>CATEGORY</strong>: Section, Curated Collection, Dynamic Collection, Collection Group, Person, Organization, Company, Place, Event, Security</li>
											<li><strong>INTERNAL DATA</strong>: Source, Author, Project, Team</li>
											<li><strong>METADATA</strong>: Image metadata, Video metadata</li>
										</ul>
