									<div class="meta__text">
									<ul>
										<li>As a user, I want to be able to publish my changes to the current content.</li>
										<li>As a user, I want to be able to save my changes to the current content as a draft.</li>
										<li>As a user, I want to see a high-fidelity preview of the content.</li>
									</ul>
									</div>
									<span class="meta__notes"><i class="fa fa-sticky-note"></i> Notes</span>
									<div class="meta__text">
										Applicable to all BEE content types:
										<ul>
